<sect1 id="REJECTED">
  <!-- DNT-Start --><title>REJECTED</title><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para><emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End --><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End --></primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End --> function</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis><emphasis>condition,...,condition</emphasis><emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <para><informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colwidth="77.90pt" />

        <colspec colwidth="274.90pt" />

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis>condition</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry>A conditional expression to evaluate.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->Return:<!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End --> returns a single value.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable></para>

  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>function evaluates which
  of the list of <emphasis>conditions</emphasis> returned false and returns
  its ordinal position in the list of <emphasis>conditions</emphasis>. Zero
  (0) returns if none return false. This is the opposite of the <!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End -->
  function<indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End --> function</primary>
    </indexterm>.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting>Rejects := REJECTED(Person.first_name &lt;&gt; 'Fred',
Person.first_name &lt;&gt; 'Sue');
// Rejects receives 0 for everyone except those named Fred or Sue
</programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para>See Also: <link linkend="WHICH"><!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="MAP"><!-- DNT-Start -->MAP<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="CHOOSE"><!-- DNT-Start -->CHOOSE<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="IF"><!-- DNT-Start -->IF<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="CASE"><!-- DNT-Start -->CASE<!-- DNT-End --></link></para>
</sect1>
